This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with image classification and pixel-labeling tasks. It also involves deep learning techniques, which are commonly used in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The concept of data-dependent routing and resource allocation is related to neural networks (cs.NE) and natural language processing (cs.CL) sub-categories.
